parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the passenger presence sensor mat can cause the airbag system to malfunction, leading to the deactivation of the passenger airbag, which can increase the risk of injury or death in the event of a crash.
symptoms: The "Service Airbag" warning light comes on
the airbag light on the dashboard illuminates
the passenger airbag status changes between on and off intermittently
the airbag warning light comes on when the passenger leaves the car
and the airbag system fails to deploy when occupied by a person of normal size.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the propulsion system can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power
the "Propulsion Power Reduced" warning message appears
the engine light turns on
the vehicle is unable to accelerate
and the vehicle may shut down while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the high voltage charging system can cause the vehicle to not charge, leading to reduced propulsion power and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: The "Service High Voltage Charging System" warning message appears
the vehicle is unable to charge
the propulsion power is reduced
and the vehicle may shut down while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the battery can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power
the battery is unable to hold a charge
the "Service High Voltage Charging System" warning message appears
and the vehicle may shut down while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the infotainment system can cause the driver to be distracted, leading to accidents.
symptoms: The infotainment screen goes blank
the vehicle's systems are unavailable
and the driver is unable to access important information.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause the airbags to not deploy in the event of an accident, leading to increased risk of injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light turns on
the passenger airbag does not deploy
and the airbag system malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The water leak can cause electrical components to malfunction, leading to increased risk of accidents or fires.
symptoms: Water leaks into the vehicle
electrical components malfunction
and the vehicle's systems are unavailable.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden loss of power or propulsion can cause the vehicle to stall or decelerate rapidly, increasing the risk of accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly loses power or propulsion
the "Propulsion Power Reduced" warning message appears on the dashboard
the vehicle decelerates rapidly
or the engine shuts down.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission or engine can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, increasing the risk of accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power
the "Engine Not Available" warning message appears on the dashboard
or the transmission fails to engage.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, increasing the risk of accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly loses power
the "Power Propulsion Reduced" warning message appears on the dashboard
or the electrical system fails to function properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the battery or charging system can cause the vehicle to lose power or stall, increasing the risk of accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The battery drains rapidly
the vehicle fails to charge
or the "Low Traction" warning message appears on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the regenerative braking system can cause the vehicle to lose braking power, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle experiences a sudden loss of braking power
the "Low Traction" warning message appears on the dashboard
or the regenerative braking system fails to function properly.
